      <h1>About Us</h1>
      <p>
        At <strong>URBAN WEAR</strong>, we are passionate about delivering high-quality contemporary fashion that empowers individuals to express their unique identity. 
        Our mission is to be the premier destination for modern streetwear, providing curated collections that inspire confidence and push the boundaries of style.
